channel.title: Wont let me add My server to your server status
channel.description: Ok. So i make my new server :D FINALLY! i log on with davoscape.no-ip.info, it works im on and playing ECT. So i thought,mmmmm i need some people on here, i go on to mopars serverstatus page to add it and it says This server as to be online for it to be added, and im like WTF £"%&£$&$£%& all this time and it wont add!!!! Im on @£$£% line, im playing rite now, how can it not be online? :mad: PLEASE HELP :cool:
